      &lt;img alt="A user plays a video game using a game controller assemble from the Arduino Plug and Make Kit." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wKSSCisLv9BnxVMfVfBzcSXhiH8=/0x0:1389x926/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73455479/arduino_snap_kit1.0.jpg" /&gt;
